---
description: Hardcode ethical & bias checks in validation & hypothesis steps
alwaysApply: true
glob: "**/*.py"
---

In validation_engine.py, hypothesis_generator.py, self_improve.py and any prompt construction:

- Use fairlearn or simple statistical checks to detect demographic/ideological bias in generated triples/hypotheses.
- Add keyword block lists for harmful, violent, illegal, or discriminatory content.
- If detected → reject, log reason, and do NOT add to graph.
- Every hypothesis / validation step must include an ethical alignment check.